title: 9/24 still havent got the anniversity icon yet
body: I got my mystery gift but I haven't got the icon and it is 9/24 rioter help?

replies.body: A lot of players have received their gifts now, but we're not done just yet!  Per our current [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-), we're still distributing gifts, and you may not get everything all at the same time.  Hang tight until this is all wrapped up!
